{"tid":958593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重慶女聖誕節跳長江輕生　身上羽絨阻沉江獲救　網民：甚麼品牌？","createTime":"2018-12-28T02:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T04:26:20.000Z","uid":66260,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b6a2d0707258dd0088188edc1a3167f9c1598d","tid":958593,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:56:02.000Z","msg":"重慶一名22歲女子在聖誕節當日（25日）一時想不開，竟在奉節縣長江大橋跳江。不過她身上的羽絨就救了她一命，讓她不至被水沒頂，並在水上漂流了約半小時。最終被警方救起的她坦言：「水太冷、不敢了。」<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者表示，該名女子落水後因為羽絨的浮力，身體並沒有立即往下沉，但可能天氣太冷，女子剛跳下水就後悔，開始往岸上游，在江裡漂流了30分鐘後終被警員救起，上岸後女子在搜救人員的身上哭泣，說自己不會再輕生了。<br />\n<br />\n據搜救的警員指，這名女子跳江輕生的原因不明，但身體沒有問題，只因為江水太冷有點受寒，警方在通報女子母親後，其母親已趕到醫院，警方仍在調查事發具體原因。<br />\n<br />\n儘管事件以女事主企圖跳橋輕生為主，但網民看到新聞後都「錯重點」，紛紛發問女子所穿的羽絨究竟是甚麼牌子，甚至還有網民表示，事件說明了穿羽絨的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n（梨視頻/聯合新聞網）<br />\n<br />\n網民熱議：<br />\n<br />\n「五分鐘，我要這個羽絨服品牌的所有信息。」<br />\n<br />\n「回去給羽絨服上兩柱香！」<br />\n<br />\n「羽絨服浮力大到底是因為充絨量多還是少？」<br />\n<br />\n「這就叫白毛浮綠水？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強國竟然有野係真既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586b9968efc9c0edbd55b4bfead7b04ad5483a93","tid":958593,"uid":107364,"like":4,"dislike":39,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:57:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38c1e13d288b142066088194a8ffc52024f53951","tid":958593,"uid":45431,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:58:27.000Z","msg":"無講過話係支那牌子喎"},{"pid":"9c6b2c780311aae320e3a078e94250e74a910134","tid":958593,"uid":80814,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"件羽絨應該唔係喺中國製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa9966b279efa9106f0117faaae6532a24cd96e","tid":958593,"uid":74908,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c6b2c780311aae320e3a078e94250e74a910134","tid":958593,"uid":80814,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"件羽絨應該唔係喺中國製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:00:55.000Z","msg":"中國製造一早爆咗炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7401c075e62b64eacc02dd108f8c96cfcc7cc439","tid":958593,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:01:42.000Z","msg":"自殺都要常識<br />\n不過支那人係冇常識架啦"},{"pid":"3b37e97d35cb4113bbf3188eb8034f6aba2248e7","tid":958593,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞定北面"},{"pid":"d296aa8baf6e2d9368f1ce2bc9a76927d131d645","tid":958593,"uid":1251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:05:02.000Z","msg":"發泡膠咪會浮囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d4476a7d9ae9c3902dfb2ad668486383df72fc","tid":958593,"uid":56636,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"白毛浮綠水笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59490432cd5227f536b9628e7f4d611e39276110","tid":958593,"uid":55533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3b37e97d35cb4113bbf3188eb8034f6aba2248e7","tid":958593,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞定北面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"加拿大鵝"},{"pid":"ef663a38c893eeff64b9bd5166415eb50b7e9ec0","tid":958593,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d5c4c9f50794f992590df6a921c6e25239e38e","tid":958593,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"似係北美製造"},{"pid":"91a5e6b8d43edf43fbf28d381869c903f5e7082e","tid":958593,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a7237374cb0fd674b4efed4a047d85